                <note rend="inline" type="source">811.24 Raw Materials/408: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in the Netherlands</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Gordon</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">The Hague</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1939-11-10T17:00:00+00:20"
                            >November 10, 1939—5 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received November 10—2:18 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>263. Department’s 137, November 8, 4 p.m. Foreign Office has informed me that it
                    is telephoning Hart in London supporting our point of view.</p>
                <p>Repeated to London.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Gordon</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
